FOR DUMMIES

move all 'vihv' folder to php include path, most likely it is '/usr/share/php'

INSTALLATION
folder 'vihv' should be in php include path

1) you can copy it defalut php include path, or
2) you can copy it anywhere you want and add vihv location to php include path in 3 ways
	- set include_path in php.ini
	- set include_path for in httpd configuration (useful for virtual hosts)
	- set include_path in your php code like this ini_set("include_path",ini_get("include_path").":/path/to/folder/that/contain/vihvFolder");
3) you can copy vihv folder to your document root